Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs22\shad1\c&H70D8FB&\fn迷你简汉真广标\b0\pos(312,420)}漫迪字幕组&@Daria拽妹黛薇儿\N\N——·@严肃活泼小kk译制·——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,最后呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}And finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会和科学和语言艺术部门合作\N{\fnArial\fs18}we will be teaming up with the Science and Language Arts departments
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,进行一次跨专业学科的吉姆丛林彩弹之旅\N{\fnArial\fs18}for an interdisciplinary field trip to Jim's Paintballing Jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们中有些人可能会觉得这活动比上课睡觉还要费力\N{\fnArial\fs18}An activity that some of you may find more taxing than sleeping through class!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,国际联盟吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um... the League of Nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}一战后成立的国际组织 二战后被联合国取代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们为什么去模拟实战呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And why are we going to engage in simulated combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只有拿着玩具枪在树林里你追我赶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because no high school education is complete until you've chased
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,高中教育才算完整吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}your fellow students around the woods with toy guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的挖苦让我发笑 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your sarcasm amuses me, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你蜷缩在隐匿处时 那番话能抚慰你\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hope it provides you comfort when you're cowering in a foxhole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我们是要去学习战争如何影响文化的各个方面\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, we're going to study how warfare impacts all aspects of culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们还需要一些家长志愿者\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, we're going to need parent volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说 如果他们有人\N{\fnArial\fs18}That is, if any of them can pull
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能自愿舍弃六位数年薪不做马屁精的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}themselves away from their six figure jobs as sycophants!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 Kevin?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸不是马屁精 D老师 他是承包商\N{\fnArial\fs18}My dad's not a sycophant, Mr. D. He's a contractor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin 你要靠近射击范围的话就得和我待在一起 行吗 孩子?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Kevin, stay close to me when you get to the paintball range, okay, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,行\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼类是把我们的海洋当成他们的私鱼厕所了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are fish using our oceans as their own private toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呕心小世界独家节目 即将为您播出\N{\fnArial\fs18}A Sick, Sad World exclusive, right after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,厕所在走廊最里边 另外大海在那边\N{\fnArial\fs18}The bathroom's down the hall, or there's an ocean that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这房间比我记忆中还让人讨厌\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ugh. This room is even geekier then I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 最大的入住率是原因之一\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm sorry, the maximum occupancy is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请从前门离开\N{\fnArial\fs18}Please exit through the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道你喜欢让我难堪还 要说一些我俩很亲近的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Look, I know how you like to embarrass me and say we're related and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可拜托你不要和爸妈说\N{\fnArial\fs18}but please don't tell Mom and Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,学校需要彩弹志愿者的事好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}that they're looking for paintball volunteers, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可我已经给他们发了邀请函啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I already sent out their invitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 你才没有呢 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ha ha. You didn't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,淡定 我们因同一个目标而协同共进:\N{\fnArial\fs18}Relax. We work together for the sake of a common goal:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们谁都不要提彩弹或志愿者的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}no mention of paintballing or volunteering from either one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\fnArial\fs18}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 等我们达成目标以后\N{\fnArial\fs18}Later, after we have achieved this goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将恢复那种长久以来\N{\fnArial\fs18}we'll resume the age-old hostilities
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都不可能在这房子里产生和平的敌意\N{\fnArial\fs18}that have made peace in this region of the house a seeming impossibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好计划\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是觉得这发型暗示着什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you think this hair style means something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它压根没暗示什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可你从来不....\N{\fnArial\fs18}But you never...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不能随心所欲试试新造型吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can't I experiment with a new look if I want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以 但我...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好呗 好呗\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,全校要去一个彩弹野战赛\N{\fnArial\fs18}The whole school's going on a paintballing field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,把火钳收起来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Put away the red-hot poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,时尚俱乐部要我负责找到一种能防止头发被头盔压塌的发型\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Fashion Club put me in charge of figuring out a style to prevent helmet hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道她们要这样做的 我承受不住所有压力\N{\fnArial\fs18}I didn't know they were going to do it! I can't take all this pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别自责了 你好好挺住十秒钟\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't beat yourself up. You held out a good ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,彩弹 多激动人心啊 对吧 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Paintballing! That's exciting, isn't it, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnArial\fs18}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 这趟出行对你来说会很有益的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, this trip would be very good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你能了解自己的校友和老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}You'll get to know your schoolmates and your teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗅到那会有很多大学的推荐信\N{\fnArial\fs18}I smell lots of recommendations for college!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真好笑\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能嗅到十五磅的魔法编织牌发胶味\N{\fnArial\fs18}All I smell is fifteen pounds of Magic Braid hair gel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那些信对你进入第一志愿的学校关系重大\N{\fnArial\fs18}Those letters can make the difference in getting into your first choice school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只有在你有第一志愿时才关系重大\N{\fnArial\fs18}Only if you have a first choice school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jake 告诉Daria - 我的天啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Jake, tell Daria... - Oh, my God,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去修一路坏到家里另一头的松塌地板啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have to fix that loose floorboard all the way at the other end of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我可能要亲自去和那些老师聊一聊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actually, I should probably deal with these teachers directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你是想帮我念完这学期吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, do you want to finish out the semester for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是一个负责任家长该做的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's what an involved parent would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妈 我觉得你已经证明你有参与其中啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mom, I think you've already demonstrated your involvement
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,每次O'Neill老师找你去家长会\N{\fnArial\fs18}by pretending you're going out of town
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你都假装出差啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}whenever Mr. O'Neill calls about school review meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男的太.... 恐怖了嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}That man is just so... creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们不需要志愿者去....\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't suppose they need volunteers for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要\N{\fnArial\fs18}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 该死\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在让我们瞧瞧车上的哪一边唱的最大声\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now lets see which side of the bus can sing the loudest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,左边\N{\fnArial\fs18}Left side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"当Johnny迈步回家时 万岁 万岁"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"When Johnny comes marching home again, hurrah, hurrah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}美国独立战争歌曲《当约翰尼迈步回家时》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 右边 别害羞\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, left side, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 O'Neill老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thank you, Mr. O'Neill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你不知疲倦的奉献和提醒学生我们有多老土\N{\fnArial\fs18}for your tireless dedication to reminding the students how out of touch we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 我们来讨论一下游击战的历史\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, we're going to discuss the history of guerilla warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"离大白鲨只有20米"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Only 20 miles to the Great White Shark."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 鲨鱼其实不喜欢吃人\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, sharks don't really like to eat humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们通常都只是浅尝辄止就游走了\N{\fnArial\fs18}They usually just tear out a bite and swim away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和我妹妹的约会情况真像\N{\fnArial\fs18}Very much like my sister's dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 当然啦 他们通常会咬走一两个重要器官...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, sure, they often take a vital organ or two with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感激你试着安慰我 不过这并不凑效\N{\fnArial\fs18}I appreciate you trying to cheer me up, but it's not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 我们来玩单词游戏嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on! Let's play a word game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,地理怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about geography?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你得玩你知道的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nah, you have to, like, know stuff for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,玩地产大亨咋样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What about Monopoly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,地产大亨不是单词游戏\N{\fnArial\fs18}Monopoly isn't a word game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我能当赛车吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can I be the racing car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这样做吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}So it's decided:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么事 我们都不要对彼此开枪也不要弄脏衣服\N{\fnArial\fs18}no matter what happens, we won't shoot each other and mess up our outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我对某个时尚俱乐部的成员开火了\N{\fnArial\fs18}If I fire on a fellow Fashion Club member,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}此地距离大白鲨只有10英里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我就得穿一个星期棕色的橡皮筋裤子\N{\fnArial\fs18}may I wear brown pants with an elastic band for a whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我开火了 我就穿灰褐色的裤袜 还是闪亮的那种\N{\fnArial\fs18}If I fire, I'll wear taupe pantyhose. The shiny kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我就穿砂洗牛仔裤\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stonewashed jeans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我戴眼镜\N{\fnArial\fs18}Glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 不要担心有人会伤害你 因为我会保护你的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, don't worry about anyone hitting you. Cause I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我是你的保镖\N{\fnArial\fs18}Me, too! I'll be your bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们得先杀了我\N{\fnArial\fs18}They'll have to kill me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真心想为你挡子弹\N{\fnArial\fs18}I really want to take a bullet for you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你挡得了的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, if only you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 所以就轮到Mack了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, so let's say it's Mack's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他说"我从没一脚踏两船"\N{\fnArial\fs18}He says, "I never went steady with two people at the same time."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后Jodie 要是你从来没有脚踏两船的话 你不用喝酒\N{\fnArial\fs18}And then Jodie, if you never went steady with two people at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用喝酒\N{\fnArial\fs18}then you don't take a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,喝什么酒啊? 我们在车上\N{\fnArial\fs18}A drink of what? We're on a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可我的意思是 要是我有一脚踏两船的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I, like, have gone steady with two people at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就得罚酒 懂了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}so I do take a drink. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我是说... 不好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, I... I mean... oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}距离大白鲨还有1英里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们甩掉彩弹野战去拜访大白鲨吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's ditch paintballing and go visit the Great White Shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,会很酷的\N{\fnArial\fs18}It'll be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:06:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 才不酷呢 会很蠢的 况且我们已经在做蠢事了\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, it won't. It'll be stupid, and we're already doing something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可那蠢事会是我们的主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}But this stupid thing will be our idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没兴趣\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这里就有很多白痴的史前生物\N{\fnArial\fs18}There are plenty of tiny-brained prehistoric creatures right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}吉姆丛林彩弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,惊喜咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What are they doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是在家里私下折磨我还不够吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess tormenting me in the privacy of my own home wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 这不是很好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前和你妈妈说了家长会的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I called your mother about the school review,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可她那晚出差了\N{\fnArial\fs18}but she was going out of town that night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还问起我们是不是需要志愿者\N{\fnArial\fs18}and asked if we were looking for paintball volunteers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望有更多的家长\N{\fnArial\fs18}I only wish more parents
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,能对"积极参与孩子的教育"这事足够重视\N{\fnArial\fs18}cared enough to take such an active role in their children education.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}吉姆丛林彩弹大型运动场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我们走得快一点 十点钟就能看到大白鲨啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}If we walk fast, we can see the Great White Shark by ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也有一个战俘监狱的复制品 臭名昭著的河内希尔顿\N{\fnArial\fs18}We also have an exact replica of 'nam's infamous POW prison, the Hanoi Hilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可享受特殊的婚礼折扣\N{\fnArial\fs18}Special discouts for weddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,上校吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Colonel, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请问女厕所在哪?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where's the ladies room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 那是有分布着一些慰安所\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, there are "comfort stations" scattered about,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不过都伪装的很好啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}but they're really well camouflaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你 过来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, you! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很厉害? 一整条迷宫状的地下通道\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isn't it great? A whole labyrinth of underground tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你能在里面迷失好几天\N{\fnArial\fs18}You could get lost down there for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 真厉害 有虫\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, great. Uck, worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住这个难得的机会 大声说\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, seize this golden opportunity to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"年轻人私密汇报 先生或女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Private Young Person reporting, sir or madam,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好愿意探索团队精神的真正意义了吗"\N{\fnArial\fs18}ready, willing, and able to explore the true meaning of teamwork."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,出发 团队\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's go, team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 Brittany\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's it, Brittany!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,红队里有谁想在出发前说点什么吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who else on Team Red wants to say something before we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane...?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jane...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 这时候团队里可没有"自我"这一说\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, Jane, there's no "I" in team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为了理解战争对自然社会的破坏性\N{\fnArial\fs18}To understand the disruptive nature of war on society,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们首先得理解它对个人的震撼影响\N{\fnArial\fs18}first we must understand its shattering impact on individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管这么假设很愚蠢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I realize it's foolish of me to assume that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝队里的任何一员都知道切肤之痛是什么感觉\N{\fnArial\fs18}any member of Team Blue even knows what physical pain feels like,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,像被纸割一样无关痛痒\N{\fnArial\fs18}outside of a paper cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对呀 真是一群...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, what a bunch of... ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 警报有误\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry. False alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你叔叔?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Eww, that's your uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 记住游戏的目的就是开枪杀戮\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, remember the object of the game is to shoot to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 游戏的目的不是夺得敌人的旗帜么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me. Isn't the object of the game to capture the enemy's flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,随便啦 行动开始\N{\fnArial\fs18}Whatever. Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 在我们上战场之前\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, before we go out on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有谁想分享一下他的感受...\N{\fnArial\fs18}would anyone like to share their feelings with...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,既然O'Neill老师如所预见般抛弃了我们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now that Mr. O'Neill has predictably deserted us in our prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在到我指挥\N{\fnArial\fs18}I will take command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 如果我们分散成长排向队旗进攻...\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, if we spread out in a long line and sweep towards the flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下 Barche老师?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me, Ms. Barch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我们有地势优势\N{\fnArial\fs18}Since they can't see us very well because of the terrain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就能分散行动 他们也发现不了我们\N{\fnArial\fs18}we can split up and they won't know where we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们能从三方进攻\N{\fnArial\fs18}then we can attack them from three sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们逼到他们以为是安全的死角\N{\fnArial\fs18}drive them out to the one side that they think is safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里设下埋伏 就能把他们一网打尽\N{\fnArial\fs18}and then set up an ambush so we can capture them all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也许在高地设一个秘密瞭望点会是一个好主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}Probably be a good idea to set up a secret observation post on the high ground
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能在他们发现不了的情况下监视他们\N{\fnArial\fs18}so we can watch them without them seeing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好极了 Brittany\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's very good, Brittany.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 蓝队 出发\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, team, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 Jane\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on Jane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我更像是个雇佣兵\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm more of the mercenary type.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 我喜欢单刀匹马自己干\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, lone wolf working on their own type of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果A计划黄了 你还能执行拯救任务呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}If Plan A fails, you can come in on a rescue mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人在开枪\N{\fnArial\fs18}The men are shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那些彩弹打人好痛啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ow! Those paintball thingies hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你被打中了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no, you're hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你出局了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're out of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子 打从一开始就没有机会\N{\fnArial\fs18}Poor kid. She never had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谁谁在电影里有句台词说 地狱就是理智的可能性\N{\fnArial\fs18}Somebody in a movie once said, hell is the possibility of sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是这地方给我的感受\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what this place feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真该死 我已经开始讨厌这儿了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hell. I hate it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,才过了一个小时\N{\fnArial\fs18}And it's only been an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的时间 奶奶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Some damn hour, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你至少回击一下吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, you could at least try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能朝我亲生母亲开枪 至少不能用油彩呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't shoot my own mother. Not with paint, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 我放弃一切来到这里\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, I'm out here giving my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪怕就一次...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why can't you for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Helen Morgendorffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 嗨 Eric\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, hi, Eric!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我是在森林中部呢 你能相信吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, I'm out here in the middle of the woods, can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,便签吗? Stephanie没有把它给你吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}The memo? Didn't Stephanie give it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事耽误你这么久?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我半路杀了一个村的农民\N{\fnArial\fs18}I stopped to wipe out a village of farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 就因为你为了他帅哥哥甩了他这事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, just because you dump a guy for his older, cuter brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他就对你怀恨在心啦?\N{\fnArial\fs18}does that give him the right to hold a grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,男人还真是有够不成熟的呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Men are so immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你造吗 要是我早知道我们要在泥地跋涉\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, if I knew we were going to be running around in the dirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不会穿名牌运动鞋来\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wouldn't have worn my good sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能闭嘴吗? 我好像看到什么了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Will you guys shut up? I think I see something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Quinn 那是你表姐吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, Quinn, is that your cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就该这么做 Quinn队长\N{\fnArial\fs18}Way to go, Quinn. Our leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 这是我新买的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, I just bought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandi? 你在这儿干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sandi? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找厕所呢 你突然就朝我开枪了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I was looking for the bathroom, and all of a sudden you started shooting at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我们说好不开火的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I thought we promised not to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会朝你开枪的 Sandi\N{\fnArial\fs18}I would never fire at you, Sandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可你戴了防护镜 我没认出来\N{\fnArial\fs18}I didn't recognize you with your goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是呀 你干嘛要穿那个啊? 丑死了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, I mean, why are you wearing them? They're so ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为规定就是要穿啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘛 有些规定就是制定来让人违反的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, some rules are made to be broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就比如穿橘色毛衣还要烈焰红唇那样\N{\fnArial\fs18}like wearing red lipstick with an orange sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有金头发还要画烟熏妆\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or black mascara with blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了 你都中弹了 还要打我们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Besides, you fired on us when you were already hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这也有违规则\N{\fnArial\fs18}and that's against the rules, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 要是你们都帮着Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gee, if everyone's on Quinn's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆让Quinn做时尚俱乐部的主席得了\N{\fnArial\fs18}maybe Quinn should be president of the Fashion Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别傻了 我才不会做主席呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't be silly. I would never try to be president,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一天有你在 都不会\N{\fnArial\fs18}as long as you were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真哒?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 你真的觉得我能取代你吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure. I mean, do you really think that I could replace you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 Kevin 你觉得你那个萎缩的豌豆般大的细胞体\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, Kevin, do you think that atrophied, pea-sized cluster of cells
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你说的"脑子"\N{\fnArial\fs18}that you refer to as your brain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能记住我刚给你下达的复杂指令吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}can remember the complicated instructions I just gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯... 夺得队旗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um... "get the flag"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 Kevin\N{\fnArial\fs18}Very good, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不准动 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}Freeze, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那彩弹打人真疼啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ow! Those paintball thingies hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我都要上绷带啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going to get a welt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,战争就是残酷的 Kevvy\N{\fnArial\fs18}War's not pretty, Kevvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉喽\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,烂死了 坏骗子 你们都是骗子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Rotten, dirtbag liars! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Barch老师 别打啦 彩弹打人可疼啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ms. Barch, stop shooting! Those paintball thingies hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亏我还相信你 该死\N{\fnArial\fs18}I trusted you, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,整整二十年的合法奴隶制\N{\fnArial\fs18}Two decades of legal slavery,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是为一件系带背心和一双小舞鞋就把它抛之脑后啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}and still you throw it all away for a halter top and a pair of pumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人 我想你一定是认错人啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Madam, I believe you've got me confused with someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是你前夫\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm not your ex-husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 可他不在这儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know that, but he's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}距离大白鲨还有3英里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 之前我还一直觉得太干燥了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good. I was feeling too dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该调头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe we should turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}大白鲨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你妈妈会借给你一件雨衣\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe your mother will lend you a raincoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖闭嘴走下去吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Shut up and keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}请勿触摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是来看大白鲨的\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're here to see the Great White Shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是杰作 不是吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, it's a beauty, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是颗牙齿\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你知道大白鲨的传说 就不会说它只是颗牙齿了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You wouldn't say, "it's a tooth," if you know the legend of Great White.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,长久以来 女人就是被设定成要隐瞒自己年龄的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Woman have been programmed to lie about their age for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得人们说四十岁看起来像五十岁\N{\fnArial\fs18}no wonder people think forty looks like fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我很欣慰那结束了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm glad that's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,阿门 感谢上帝 男人不再把我们看作是发泄兽欲的对象\N{\fnArial\fs18}Amen! Thank God men no longer look at us like sex objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,言之有理 妹子\N{\fnArial\fs18}You said it, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那我看起来是不是有46... 44岁?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So do I look forty si... four?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 介意我... - 想都别想 你这男人\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Would you like my... - Forget it, you man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可我只是想给你我的...\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I was just offering my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,浪费老娘22年青春 一走了之\N{\fnArial\fs18}Twenty two years of my life, gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}河内希尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你所展现出来的照顾\N{\fnArial\fs18}And all I have to show for tending to your every need
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就只有我脚上的鸡眼和胸上的皮疹\N{\fnArial\fs18}are the corns on my feet and a big rash on my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,继续 没关系的 都发泄出来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Go ahead, it's all right. Let it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 你为什么不带着你的好战性\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, why don't you just go back outside
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,出去破坏些脆弱的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}with your war mongering sex and destroy something weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,宣泄会让你感觉良好 是吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Venting feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝对有权利感到愤怒 并释放出来\N{\fnArial\fs18}You have every right to feel angry, and to express that anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 外面倾盆大雨呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hi! It's raining cats and dogs out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下是多么独特的视角\N{\fnArial\fs18}What a unique perspective on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喝点暖暖身吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Little nip to warm you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer先生 我是一名教师\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mr. Morgendorffer, I'm a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要在一次相当危险的实地考察中对学生负责\N{\fnArial\fs18}responsible for dozens of students on a fairly hazardous filed trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我能喝吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you think I should take a little nip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想还是算了吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我想还是不要算了 快给我\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, I guess not! Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你是不是上过军校呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Say, did you, by any chance, go to military school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How'd you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在大白鲨被捕的两个月以前\N{\fnArial\fs18}Until Great White was captured two months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他威吓东海岸\N{\fnArial\fs18}he terrorized the eastern seaboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,把旅客嚼进嘴里 又像喝了坏红酒那样把他们吐出来\N{\fnArial\fs18}chomping on tourists and spitting them out like bad red wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是旅游旺季\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was the peak of tourist season,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当一具残缺的尸体被冲上海岸时\N{\fnArial\fs18}when a mangled body washed up on the shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沙滩上的流浪者都吓坏了...\N{\fnArial\fs18}scaring the beachcombers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你更喜欢我们俩中的谁?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Which one of us do you like best?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们谁想带我去Chez Pierre夜店?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Which one of you wants to take me to Chez Pierre?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll take you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 我来 我有钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, no, me! I've got the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn真是太萌了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,比我还萌?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cuter than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 你萌多了啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no. You're way cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,外表不是最重要的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not that looks are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我能找到厕所\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wish I could find that bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是在那边的某个地方\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think it's over there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandi去哪啦?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where's Sandi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的啦 Sandi嘛 总是去找厕所的路上\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, you know Sandi. Always looking for a bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她今天特别萌\N{\fnArial\fs18}She looks really cute today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,比我还萌吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cuter than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 你萌多了嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no. You're way cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,市长称那些残骸都是螺旋桨的受害者\N{\fnArial\fs18}the mayor claimed that the chewed-up bodies were the victims of a propeller,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但老百姓才不会上当\N{\fnArial\fs18}but the people knew better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思呀 这不是电影《大白鲨》的桥段吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me, but isn't this the plot of Jaws?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 这完全不同呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, no! This is completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那时他们把捕鲨人叫来了\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's when they called in the great shark hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那时他们叫来了... 我\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's when they called in... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer太太 看到你如此关心你的女儿们 我很欣慰\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm glad to see you take such an interest in your daughters, Mrs. Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,独自养大两个青少年真的很不容易... 还是和Jake一起\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, it isn't easy raising two teenagers all by yourself... with Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦 我觉得学校环境也是很重要的因素\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course, I like to think the school environment also plays a pivotal role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然给予学生更多一点鼓励会更好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Although it would be nice if the students got a little more encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也许像Daria这么聪明的孩子态度就会更好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe a bright kid like Daria would have a better attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了什么那么好笑?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did I say something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言\N{\fnArial\fs18}With all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想象不出有什么监狱能培养出令千金那种态度了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't think of a prison that could create an attitude like your daughter's,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,更别说学校\N{\fnArial\fs18}much less a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我经常假设这是源于和父母的互动 或是缺乏交流\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, I always assumed that came from interaction with her parents, or lack of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 所以按你这么说 监狱和学校是有区别的喽\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, so you draw a distinction between prison and school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为据我知 你把学校搞的和监狱差不多\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because from what I've heard, you run the one pretty much like the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我压根不用听这话\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't have to listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是 你是不用\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便多说一句 你看起来有50岁\N{\fnArial\fs18}And by the way, you look fifty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过用鱼叉捕它\N{\fnArial\fs18}I tried harpooning Great White,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但那巨兽像甩牙签一样把鱼叉甩掉了\N{\fnArial\fs18}but the massive beast shook them off like so many toothpicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过用浮桶把它拖下来 可还是不行\N{\fnArial\fs18}I tried tying him down with floating barrels, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大白鲨说"我才不受这些控制" 所以船长就决定...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Great White said, "I will have none of this!" So the captain decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,雨小点儿了 我们走吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}The rain's letting up. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后那小鼻涕虫Richard Dreyfuss决定他自己要露一手....\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then that little snot Richard Dreyfuss decides that it was all his big game...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和另一半签订婚前协议前 不先和自己签一份\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just what good is signing a prenuptial agreement with another
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,又有什么意义呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}if we don't first sign one with ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没想过会有这种事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I never thought it possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你真体恤 尽管你是个男人\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're sensitive, yet you're a male.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 好吧...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小心皮疹...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Watch the rash...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不想重蹈我爸的覆辙\N{\fnArial\fs18}I didn't mean to step on Dad's contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天 他就把我送去军校了\N{\fnArial\fs18}The next day, he shipped me off to military school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈不想让她的情夫们知道她有个拖油瓶\N{\fnArial\fs18}My mother didn't want her dates to know she had a son,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我经常待在邻居家 奇怪又扭曲的邻居\N{\fnArial\fs18}so I spent a lot of time at the neighbors. Strange, twisted people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂 我也有这样的邻居\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know! I had the same neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 你喝醉了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake! You're drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,醉了? 别傻啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Drunk? Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 快来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 我们要走啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn! We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,回来呀 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come back Quinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 快回来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"当Jonny迈步回家的时候 万岁 万岁"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"When Johnny comes marching home again, hurrah, hurrah..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 每个人都到齐了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, is everyone accounted for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 那就准备走吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes. Okay, time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我没看到你们爸妈\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait! I don't see the Morgendorffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那你又能怎么办\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well, what can you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了 他们是自己开车来的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Besides, they drove here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能自己开车回去\N{\fnArial\fs18}They can drive themselves home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 如果没人把他们的分火盖偷走的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}That is, if someone hadn't taken their distributor cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,当你要告诉妹子们你会对她们有所承诺\N{\fnArial\fs18}Drinking on a school trip when you're supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你就得在全校出游时期喝酒\N{\fnArial\fs18}to be showing the girls that you're committed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,承诺? 我承诺过 好啦 我是从来没受过考验啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Committed? Oh, I've been committed, all right, and I never even had a trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等我有足够空间来重装子弹\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just wait till I have enough room to reload!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别啊 Helen 彩弹打得我好痛啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}No! Helen! Those paintball thingies hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怕... 好可怕...\N{\fnArial\fs18}The horror... the horror...
